---------------------
CD/DVD viewer

- X ray facilities start handing CD/DVD to people with
  their studies on them
- the included browser, however, only runs on windows
- so, on linux provide the following:
- function "browse CD/DVD"
  - scan all files on media
  - match against known list of useful mime types
    (gif, jpeg, png, mpeg, dicom, etc)
  - display known useful files in flat list
  - let user select a file
  - start viewer via mailcap

